text: Aidhausen is a municipality in Haßberge in Bavaria in Germany, it is a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft Hofheim in Unterfranken. == Geography == Aidhausen is in the Main-Rhön region. It is divided into the following districts: Aidhausen, Friesenhausen, Happertshausen, Kerbfeld and Nassach. ==References== == Other websites == * * Category:Haßberge (district)
